Java Intro:
----------------
Imagine this.

You wake up in the morning.
Your alarm rings.
You unlock your phone.
Order breakfast.
Travel to office.
Attend online meetings.
Swipe your card.
Watch a movie at night.

You just used Javaâ€¦ without writing a single line of it.

Why does world trust Java?
Stable - Systems runs for years without crashing.
Secure - Java has security layers that cant be break easily
Scalable - Even your app/website traffic goes from 10 users to a million users, Java has good features to handles your app work smoothly. 
Portable - Write once and run anywhere.


Smartphones: 
  All your apps in IOS or Android uses java.
Banks & Financial systems: 
   t/f money, swiping a card, processing some transaction ex. NEFT.
Airlines and Railways: 
   Ticket booking, seat allocation, reservations, feedback systems.
Smart Devices & Tv's:
   smart TV's or android TV's, barcode scanners.
Cars & IOT:
   Self driving cars & music systems.

Java lives in all these places.

Download the below tools.
IntelliJ Idea - https://www.jetbrains.com/idea/download/?section=windows
